---
It's another Monday
The train already opened
It's cold
My mouth tastes bitter
My head is spinning 
My eyes are burning
And my migraines are killing me 
But
I have to go to work.
...
I feel so lonely
...
Everyone is far
And I have less time
...
...
How many times I was in this train?
...
I don't know
...
Everytime I was out 
Everytime I visit my friends
Everytime I went to college
Everytime I took care of my mother

===
